empowering officers to protect

00:01:52.780 --> 00:01:56.740
customer rights and handle complaints
according to consumer laws.

00:01:57.220 --> 00:02:02.380
It is also key for fraud prevention,
giving folks the know-how to identify

00:02:02.380 --> 00:02:06.429
and act against nasty financial
crimes like money laundering.

00:02:06.820 --> 00:02:10.240
Let's not forget contract
management, which is essential

00:02:10.240 --> 00:02:14.440
for understanding and actually
enforcing agreements with customers.

00:02:14.829 --> 00:02:19.540
