Here are some methods to
solve it systematically.

00:05:35.190 --> 00:05:38.040
First, practice keyword identification.

00:05:38.610 --> 00:05:42.420
Read the question like a detective
and pull out the core legal

00:05:42.420 --> 00:05:47.635
keywords such as check contract,
loan default, or consumer dispute.

00:05:48.480 --> 00:05:52.620
Once you have your keyword, the
next step is act association.

00:05:53.100 --> 00:05:57.000
