is your best friend.

00:06:18.115 --> 00:06:22.315
Get rid of the options that are
obviously silly or irrelevant

00:06:22.315 --> 00:06:23.545
to the legal situation.

00:06:23.995 --> 00:06:26.575
Also, use contextual analysis.

00:06:27.115 --> 00:06:31.585
Pay attention to the details in the
scenario given as they can completely

00:06:31.585 --> 00:06:34.105
change how a legal principle applies.

00:06:34.525 --> 00:06:40.255
And of course, for some questions, it's
just about direct recall definition or

00:06:40.315 --> 00:06:44.995
ear based questions often just need you to
pull the fact straight from your memory.

