have very precise legal meanings,

00:08:45.840 --> 00:08:50.760
and a classic error is memorizing
incorrect ears for important acts.

00:08:51.090 --> 00:08:54.750
Finally, a big one is
overlooking amendments.

00:08:55.020 --> 00:08:56.100
Laws change.

